\DOC ml_dir_pathname

\TYPE {ml_dir_pathname : string}

\SYNOPSIS
Absolute pathname to the HOL ML sources.

\DESCRIBE
For implementation reasons, the ML variable {ml_dir_pathname} is bound when
the system if built to a string giving the absolute pathname of the directory
containing the HOL ML sources.  This value is not for general use.

\FAILURE
Evaluating {ml_dir_pathname} never fails.

\SEEALSO
lisp_dir_pathname.

\ENDDOC
